{"tid":1190731,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"n賓又出事","createTime":"2019-06-07T13:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:31:24.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad786fb40f6c77bde56cb5869d7f4494eb5c4a2","tid":1190731,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"早上10時44分，西貢伙頭墳洲香港晨曦會戒毒所兩名男院友，在院舍內除草期間，其中姓鍾（25歲）院友被青竹蛇咬傷右腳腳指，另一院友見狀報警，約半小時後，4名男院友（年齡27至50歲）用三輪車載送鍾往伙頭墳洲碼頭等候救援期間，三輪車突失控撞向一草叢，5人全部受傷，被蛇咬傷腳的鍾傷上加傷，可謂禍不單行，而姓吳（49歲）院友更被蜜蜂刺傷。鍾與另一名院友先行由政府飛行服務隊吊送往東區醫院救治，其餘3名車禍中傷者，送到水警東基地，再由救護車送往將軍澳醫院治理。"},{"pid":"40bc86814df10bb2c1e768dae3cb8ea3463809ce","tid":1190731,"uid":197364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"三輪車出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98b9e75060e03154a8af6ecd5981c1027896458","tid":1190731,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"呢個係拉車"},{"pid":"5b13dc1a4b5c109bacce75731f087d166eea3bef","tid":1190731,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"關n賓咩事？"},{"pid":"cada230012ee826b245cd9490df06c0bdfba68dd","tid":1190731,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"連炒車都要屈埋nben<br />\nNben既負擔實在太重了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bf079d5f01361f2507253891a3528debcd42e1","tid":1190731,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b13dc1a4b5c109bacce75731f087d166eea3bef","tid":1190731,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"關n賓咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"戒毒所院友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9798ca8c95d65ed88df6b24c3a48d813bc70575","tid":1190731,"uid":214972,"li